I don't have an 'install' file/folder showing up once I've done the install and so I'm not sure where to put the crack file.  Does it just go into the Revo Uninstaller Pro folder?

@trinity8 Unrar the regular Revo Unin. Pro and install it (remember the directory where it went). Open it after installation. Go to tools, then into options, then uncheck the update box. Now CLOSE THE PROGRAM. Go into the crack folder and copy the Revo Pro in there and paste-replace it into where the regular Revo is.
